# Feature Development Process

## Initial Setup
1. Create necessary directories (components, modals)
2. Set up basic component structure
3. Implement UI framework before adding logic

## Component Development
1. Start with basic UI implementation
2. Add state management
3. Implement business logic
4. Add error handling
5. Implement loading states
## Testing
1. Test UI responsiveness
2. Test dark mode
3. Test error states
4. Test loading states
